  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "ufo contact",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "113",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "EDITORIAL...",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "\"WE ARE NOT OPPOSED TO A COURT JESTER",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "on the green lawns of the Royal Palace, provided he",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "is not taken for an astronomical philosopher - -\".",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Here, with all the arrogance of the self-opinion-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "ated, self-appointed judge, in words of ignorance,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "mated with bigotry and begotten of an inflated ego-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "tism, we see a small section of that vociferous but",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "often influential Press opinion which always swallows",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "before it chews.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "The occasion was the much-publicised, much-criti-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "cised audience of Queen Juliana of the Netherlands",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "accorded to one George Adamski of California,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "U.S.A., at 11 a.m. on May 18th 1959, at Soestdijk",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Palace, near Utrecht, Holland.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "The vociferous Press opinion in this instance was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "of the Catholic People's Party newspaper, \"Die",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Volkskrant\".",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "We could imagine the same self-elevated journa-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "list writing: \"We are not opposed to a court jester",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "in the private apartments at the Vatican, provid-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "ed - -\", on another May day, of another 11 a.m. au-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "dience, much more secret, of much more potential",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "significance, four years later, when Adamski was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "received at the bed-side of the dying Pope John.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Of the one audience, with a gracious First Lady,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "the world's sensation tabloids went to town. Lacking",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "the meat of the occasion on which to feast their",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "readers they gave them the bones and the offal, and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "in the process they soiled and besmirched their own",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "honourable profession.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "The second audience was spared this treatment,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "and still is.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "And so we can perceive how some of George",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "Adamski's meetings with the famous received the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "full blast of publicity, whilst others, conducted in a",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "secret undercurrent of diplomacy peopled with silent",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "couriers and intercontinental briefings, are still, very",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "much, \"classified\".",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "Adamski was NEVER afraid of the scoffers and the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "critics, still less of the faceless spokesmen in autho-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "rity. With energy which had to be seen to be be-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "lieved, with courage of conviction based in sure",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "knowledge of his own experiences, and with fortitude",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "distilled from the sweat and the sour of his support-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "ers and his detractors, HE DIDN'T GIVE A DAMN.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "He could have written \"pot-boilers\" of space-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "fiction in his sunny California, like many of his cont-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "emporaries, making a fortune from the credulous.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "This is shown by the fact that his books became",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "world best-sellers in many languages. Yet in 12 years",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "he only offered TWO AND A HALF BOOKS to the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "general public. Does this seem like a man who is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "\"on the make?\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "No. Instead he pushed and shoved his way, the,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "many times, inhospitable climate of \"expert\" analysis",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "and clinical dissection, saying: \"Here is my evid-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "ence, here is my story - TAKE IT OR LEAVE IT!\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "AND HE DIED, DOING JUST THAT.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "What kept him going for so long? What kept the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "flame so bright for those 12-13 long, bitter-sweet",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "years? His tremendous sense of humour? YES! His",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "many thousands of friends and supporters the world",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "over? YES, THESE ALSO!",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "But his faith in a DIVINE INTELLIGENCE and sure",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "knowledge of the existence and the helpful presence",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "friends from other planets in space, were the Rod",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "of good, spiritually- and physically-healthy human",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "and the Staff on which he leaned, until he died.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "G.A.'s \"end\" was but a beginning. And when he",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "\"graduated\" others took over.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "He knew, in those last few months, that it wouldn't",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "be long. Already he knew those who were going to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "carry on his work. And the Brothers and the Sisters,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "those friends from across the seas of space, were",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "busy in their task of forging new links, reshaping",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "the pattern of their contacts with those close to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "Adamski.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "AS WITH GEORGE ADAMSKI, the Brothers cont-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "inue to furnish evidence of their presence in our",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "skies. New films, startling in their clarity, are being",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "provided by G.A.'s Co-workers. New accounts of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "recent contact with the men and women visiting us",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "are evidence of their continued interest in our wel-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "fare.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "Here, in this issue of UFO CONTACT, you will",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "see more photographic presentation of \"Unidentified",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "Flying Objects\". In some strange fashion, by some",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "peculiar \"co-incidence\", another of G.A.'s close",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "associates is enabled to take startling movie-film",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "shots of objects in the sky. With this new evidence",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "we shall show, too, how Adamski's successors are",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "text": "STILL pushing the experts, STILL offering for exam-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "text": "ination photographic proof of \"inexplicable phenom-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "text": "ena\" in the skies above us.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "There are always those who are ready to jeer and",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "deride. This is a peculiar facet of the human psycho-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "logy which stems almost solely from ignorance. But,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "text": "thank God, there are those also who, in the face of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "text": "public intolerance and apathy, are able to stand out",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "from the rest and say of the pioneer: \"Give the man",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "his chance, let the man have his say\".",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "text": "As we have said a few words back, evidence is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "still being provided of our extraterrestrial visitors'",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "presence on and above our planet. That this evid-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "ence remains a puzzle, - or gives the impression, at",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "text": "least, of remaining a puzzle - to competent \"ex-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "text": "perts\", despite public pronouncements made by the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "text": "head of Project Blue Book, the U.S.A.F.'s UFO",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "text": "agency, that UFO's are NOT from Outer Space,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 134,
      "text": "(\"Evening Telegram\", San Bernadino, California,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 135,
      "text": "February 15th 1967 - full report on Page 103, UFO",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "text": "CONTACT, April issue), is shown here in the pages",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "text": "of UFO CONTACT.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    }
